[h3 
	"About the strategy
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"I didn't struggled much for understanding the game mechanics. All I did was trying to manipulate the enemy behaviour better. I tried to hit both enemies with the first attack, as it's the most obvious time save, but I couldn't do in all stages, due to the different enemy behaviour.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"I had to wait some frames before enterting stage 4 in order to manipulate RNG.
	$LF
